short_desc: FRMDATEC1L must not be from date before form was released
full_desc: Q0a. FRMDATEC1L (C1L form date) must not be from date before form was released (2017)

full_desc: If Q2a. LBNPFACE is in (0-7) and Q2b. LBNPNOIS is in (0-13), Q2c. LBNPTCOR must equal Q2a. LBNPFACE + Q2b. LBNPNOIS
test_logic: If LBNPFACE in (0-7) and LBNPNOIS in (0-13) and LBNPTCOR ne LBNPFACE + LBNPNOIS

short_desc: If LBNPNOIS is in (0-13) and LBNPPARD is in (0-13), then LBNPNOIS + LBNPPARD must = 13
full_desc: If Q2b. LBNPNOIS is in (0-13) and Q2d. LBNPPARD is in (0-13), then Q2b. LBNPNOIS + Q2d. LBNPPARD must = 13
test_logic: If LBNPNOIS in (0-13) and LBNPPARD is in (0-13) and LBNPNOIS + LBNPPARD ne 13
